  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\"><img alt=\"Moon Brothers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/50px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/75px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/100px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Umar</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\"><img alt=\"Moon Brothers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/50px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/75px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ab/Moon_Brothers.svg/100px-Moon_Brothers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\">Moon Brothers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ulf\" title=\"Ulf\">Ulf</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Umar</b> is the father of <a href=\"/index.php/Ulf\" title=\"Ulf\">Ulf</a>, a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Brothers\" title=\"Moon Brothers\">Moon Brothers</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if Umar is still alive or not.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Umar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, Tyrion VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403115414\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.069 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.258 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 418/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10376/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4671/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 233/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.33 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTrans